se affecting all cartservice operations that depend on it.",\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_redis_performance",\n    "reason": "Redis-cart operations show significant latency degradation that directly correlates with cartservice endpoint slowdowns",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["redis_cpu_usage", "redis_memory_usage", "redis_connections"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["redis-cart", "slowlog", "timeout"]\n  }\n}\n```'}
